      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go. It\u2019s been kept in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no spills, just pure driving bliss. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take a look and fall in love!",
