    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is, quite simply, the finest example of this model you will find on the market today. Kept in a climate-controlled garage and covered since day one, the exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Every body panel is original, and the factory wheels are free of even the slightest curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the leather remains supple with no bolster wear, the stitching is crisp, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. All electronics, buttons, and displays function flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history with every maintenance milestone performed ahead of schedule. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is as clean as the day it left the assembly line. This is a true collector-grade vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
