    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rod bearings were proactively replaced with treated shells. The rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been professionally reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory variable M-differential. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings throughout, providing the telepathic steering response these cars are known for. No pixel failure, no subframe cracks, and zero deferred maintenance.",
